Package pda.control

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IApplication
    Common interface for all plugable applications.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ApercuCtrl
    ApercuCtrl is the listener of the ApercuView, the survey.
    ChooseCtrl
    ChooseCtrl is the listener of the ChoosePhotoView
    EditCtrl
    EditCtrl is the listener of the EditView, the edition interface
    GalleryCtrl
    GalleryCtrl is the listener of the GalleryView, the gallery of the saved images
    HelloCtrl
    The simplest application in the PDA.
    LaunchCtrl
    The "LaunchCtrl" application that starts all others.
    ListenHome
    ApercuCtrl is the listener of the PhotoBoostView, the main page
    ParamCtrl
    ParamCtrl is the listener of the ParamView
    PdaCtrl
    The base class of PDA simulator.
    PhotoBoostCtrl
    The PhotoBoostCtrl is the controler allowing to add the application to the PDA
    It implements IApplication and define all of the needed methods
